{"tid":1328288,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有條新戰線想提供，唔知work唔work，唔消費一星期","createTime":"2019-07-18T01:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T03:30:53.000Z","uid":264978,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8d337ab6da427f0e2f3c2d10ea33b88614ed4f","tid":1328288,"uid":264978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:06:47.000Z","msg":"作為一個使錢最叻嘅和理非，我覺得最有力嘅反抗（其實我已經次次都有出嚟行，做好文宣推廣，簽petition同捐錢，投訴新城市），就係停止一切非必要嘅消費。<br />\n<br />\n啱啱出咗個零售報告，已經有人驚情況再差落去，香港經濟會見紅。再加上新鴻基一副「你吹得我脹咩」嘅態度，我覺得200萬+嘅人如果肯夾埋一齊，停晒全部非必要開支，都應該起到啲作用，嚇到吓人。<br />\n<br />\n但由於擔心會影響到打工仔嘅生計，唔建議進行太長，可以試吓停一星期，試一試個反應先。如果真係得，可能會多一個籌碼响手。<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到要做嘅：<br />\n1. 訂出時間，預留時間做文宣，同埋嚇吓班商佬；<br />\n2. 列出重點要不消費嘅地方、商戶；<br />\n3. 要照顧返啲小商戶，鼓勵大家如果要消費，可以去小商戶同支持行動嘅商戶度幫襯；<br />\n4. 可以嘅話，樓都唔好買住。<br />\n<br />\n本人只係識諗，吹雞能力欠奉；如有巴絲打覺得可行，隨便攞條橋去用啦。"},{"pid":"482d2f926ebeed9c8450cde29be49c286f548f05","tid":1328288,"uid":73826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T01:07:27.000Z","msg":"【\b721文宣】星期日前一齊做鍵盤戰士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1327641\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1327641</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HXAdLRx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHXAdLRx.jpg&h=988ba3dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aw6P3Dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faw6P3Dd.jpg&h=545a2bea&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxBsQid.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxBsQid.jpg&h=0a25f5ce&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DEt65Rz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDEt65Rz.png&h=d8e97094&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vHzvie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7vHzvie.jpg&h=38ca5e73&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFsr5Rz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: